{"word":"Aaron","slug":"aaron","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Aaron</b> - son of Amram, the first high priest.<p/><b>(1)</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=14'>Exo 4:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5&verse=20'>Exo 5:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=20'>Exo 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=1'>Exo 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=7'>Exo 7:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=12'>Exo 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=1'>Exo 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=34'>Exo 16:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=12'>Exo 17:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=24'>Exo 19:24</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=14'>Exo 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=12'>Exo 28:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=10'>Exo 30:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=2'>Exo 32:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=6'>Lev 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=1'>Num 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=11'>Num 16:11</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=17&verse=3'>Num 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=25'>Num 20:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=28'>Num 20:28</a><p/><b>(2)</b> FACTS CONCERNING<p/>Made spokesman for Moses<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=1'>Ex 7:1</a><p/>With Hur, supports Moses' hands during a battle<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=12'>Ex 17:12</a><p/>Made the High Priest<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=1'>Ex 28:1</a><p/>Broke the covenant and made the Golden Calf<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=2'>Ex 32:2-4</a><p/>Excluded from the Promised Land<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=12'>Nu 20:12</a><p/>Died on Mount Hor<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=28'>Nu 20:28</a>"}]}